{"componentChunkName":"component---antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/en/docs/other/version-upgrade","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Choerodon UI","githubUrl":"https://github.com/open-hand/choerodon-ui","docs":[]},"pathPrefix":"/choerodon-ui"},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"dependency-version-check\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dependency-version-check\" aria-label=\"dependency version check permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Dependency Version Check</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the command <code class=\"language-text\">yarn list choerodon-ui</code> to check if the project version is correct and if there are any multi-version conflicts.</li>\n<li>\n<p>If multi-version conflicts occur, it indicates that there may be multiple versions of choerodon-ui specified in the package.json.\nHandling steps:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Correct the version in the package.json file, use <code class=\"language-text\">resolutions</code> for multiple versions if necessary.</li>\n<li>Remove choerodon-ui version declarations from the yarn.lock file.</li>\n<li>Delete the .cache folder in node_modules (also delete .cache under sub-services if necessary).</li>\n<li>Reinstall packages and run the project.\nThe version check flowchart is as follows:</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<img src='https://hsop-image-host.su.bcebos.com/team/3/HSOP-BAIDU/5929798ac5e741299245c466d3ad6d38@依赖版本检查.png' alt=\"Dependency Version Check.png\" />\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"version-testing-verification-of-new-version-features-or-issues\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#version-testing-verification-of-new-version-features-or-issues\" aria-label=\"version testing verification of new version features or issues permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Version Testing: Verification of New Version Features or Issues</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Precondition: Ensure the version is correct and the .cache folder in node_modules has been deleted before rerunning.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"verify-if-new-version-featuresfunctionality-or-bug-fixes-are-effective\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#verify-if-new-version-featuresfunctionality-or-bug-fixes-are-effective\" aria-label=\"verify if new version featuresfunctionality or bug fixes are effective permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Verify if new version features/functionality or bug fixes are effective</h2>\n<p>Test separately for functionality and styling.</p>\n<h3 id=\"new-version-features-and-functionality\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-version-features-and-functionality\" aria-label=\"new version features and functionality permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>New Version Features and Functionality</h3>\n<p>Basic usage:</p>\n<p>You can refer to the official website and the Choerodon-UI source project demos for usage verification.</p>\n<h4 id=\"verification-of-new-features-and-functionality\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#verification-of-new-features-and-functionality\" aria-label=\"verification of new features and functionality permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Verification of New Features and Functionality</h4>\n<p>Check if it is a code writing issue. If the code is correct, provide the code that reproduces the problem and report it to the component library maintenance team for fixing.</p>\n<h4 id=\"verification-of-function-fixes\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#verification-of-function-fixes\" aria-label=\"verification of function fixes permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Verification of Function Fixes</h4>\n<p>Attempt to reproduce the issue on the page where the bug appears.</p>\n<p>a. If the issue does not reproduce in the new version and other operations are unaffected by unrelated bugs — fix is successful.</p>\n<p>b. If the issue persists in the new version and reproduces on the official website, contact the component library maintainer (via ticket replies, enterprise WeChat, etc.).</p>\n<p>The testing flowchart is as follows:\n<img src='https://hsop-image-host.su.bcebos.com/team/3/HSOP-BAIDU/3e72e9d1f3e44bc29bf78cf748a3b551@版本测试.png' alt=\"Version Test Flowchart.png\"/></p>\n<h3 id=\"style-aspect\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-aspect\" aria-label=\"style aspect permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style Aspect</h3>\n<h4 id=\"style-issue-troubleshooting-process\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-issue-troubleshooting-process\" aria-label=\"style issue troubleshooting process permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style Issue Troubleshooting Process</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Try to reproduce the issue under the official Whale Blue theme on the website. If it reproduces, report the front-end component via a ticket or Issue.</li>\n<li>\n<p>If the style works fine in the Whale Blue theme but has problems in other themes, follow the troubleshooting approach below:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Ice White, Aurora Blue, Windbell Purple, Lark Blue:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Check if the UED style package version needs updating (steps can be found in H-ZERO's different versions and UED package dependency relationships).</li>\n<li>If the issue still exists in the latest UED style package, report the front-end component via a ticket or Issue.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Peacock Blue:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>H-ZERO version is too old: Upgrade the H-ZERO version or apply local global style overrides (refer to Peacock Blue theme style fix example).</li>\n<li>Style issues in the latest version: Report to H-ZERO via a ticket.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"style-issue-troubleshooting-diagram\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-issue-troubleshooting-diagram\" aria-label=\"style issue troubleshooting diagram permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style Issue Troubleshooting Diagram</h4>\n<img src='https://hsop-image-host.su.bcebos.com/team/3/HSOP-BAIDU/b3c65549abcf40dd8c72e7aae486e934@样式问题定位.png' alt=\"Style Issue Troubleshooting.png\" />\n<h4 id=\"style-fix-example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style-fix-example\" aria-label=\"style fix example permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style Fix Example:</h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In an older version of an H-ZERO project, after upgrading the component library, style issues appear under the Peacock Blue theme.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Method:\nThe front-end inspects the styles, identifies the specific modification points, and applies fixes in the project path src/global.module.less.</li>\n<li>Example: Incorrect rendering of required *\nIllustration as below:</li>\n</ul>\n<img src='https://hsop-image-host.su.bcebos.com/team/3/HSOP-BAIDU/2e6b969d71474d719a4f2b175526ae7c@样式修复案例图.png' alt=\"Style Fix Example.png\" width=\"100%\" />\n<p>Related code locations for style fixes:\n<img src='https://hsop-image-host.su.bcebos.com/team/3/HSOP-BAIDU/a1b254c49f3140c7a17860199ea5a4eb@样式修复代码书写位置.png' alt=\"Location for Writing Style Fix Code.png\" /></p>\n<h4 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h4>\n<h1 id=\"basic-dependencies-between-h-zero-versions-and-ued-versions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#basic-dependencies-between-h-zero-versions-and-ued-versions\" aria-label=\"basic dependencies between h zero versions and ued versions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic Dependencies Between H-ZERO Versions and UED Versions</h1>\n<p>After upgrading the component library version, some features may have style issues (inconsistent with the official site), requiring an update of the UED dependency package to the specified version.</p>\n<h2 id=\"version-relationships\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#version-relationships\" aria-label=\"version relationships permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Version Relationships</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>For H-ZERO 1.8.x and above, upgrade the @hzero-front-ui/cfg dependency package to the latest 4.x version</li>\n<li>For H-ZERO 1.7.x and above, upgrade the @hzero-front-ui/cfg dependency package to the latest 3.x version</li>\n<li>For H-ZERO versions below 1.7.x, upgrade @hzero-front-ui/c7n-ui, @hzero-front-ui/hzero-ui, and @hzero-front-ui/cfg to the latest 2.x versions</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"checking-the-latest-package-version\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#checking-the-latest-package-version\" aria-label=\"checking the latest package version permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Checking the Latest Package Version</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\">npm view <span class=\"token keyword\">package</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>name <span class=\"token function\">versions</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span>registry <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>registry<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>url<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"